hopobject.body: How many days will it take for the cheque to clear? texas pharmacy foundation scholarship No bra, no problem! Check out which celebs we've spotted going bra-free ... What a view! The Victoria's Secret stunner was using just her hands and arms for coverage during the shoot which lead to more than a few slip ups.
